{"tid":627302,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局今晨再度買入港元，兩次合共３２﹒５８億","createTime":"2018-04-13T00:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T01:53:31.000Z","uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"24459d6ee89492b3fbf5e9da40b0d4a9c14e4552","tid":627302,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T00:21:57.000Z","msg":"【港匯弱勢】金管局今晨再度買入港元，兩次合共３２﹒５８億<br />\n以更佳效果檢視 &raquo;<br />\n　　《經濟通通訊社１３日專訊》港元匯價觸發７﹒８５弱方兌換保證，金管局昨晚約８時入市承接港元沽盤，為２００５年設立雙邊兌換保證以來首次，買入８﹒１６億港元，今日清晨時間再度入市承接港元沽盤，買入２４﹒４２億港元，以維持港元匯價穩定。金管局兩次入市合共買入３２﹒５８億港元。　　美元兌港元最新報７﹒８４９８，一年電期報－５８７﹒４５╱－５６７﹒５５。　　下周一（１６日）本港銀行體系結餘總額減少至１７６５﹒２０億港元。（ｅｃ）<br />\n<br />\n🤔"},{"pid":"475c46b83e4abcda231108074c3374ae805da131","tid":627302,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T00:22:29.000Z","msg":"好快要加息"},{"pid":"f84985963bff04a0e6d9fe60c8439a69058bc431","tid":627302,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T00:22:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf6a7e105d7112a095e79a83454a9e6d4d178ee","tid":627302,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T00:23:44.000Z","msg":"加息前準備？"},{"pid":"b72d153c86a3cb09a626ebe2953f4dc0c2ecdcfd","tid":627302,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T00:23:51.000Z","msg":"邊個成日凌晨3 4點先黎沽？🤔"},{"pid":"d5b43758a7b6c638bbfc7747ad1a43b00d3dacf0","tid":627302,"uid":125731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b72d153c86a3cb09a626ebe2953f4dc0c2ecdcfd","tid":627302,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T00:23:51.000Z","msg":"邊個成日凌晨3 4點先黎沽？🤔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T00:25:52.000Z","msg":"因為外國中午？？"},{"pid":"d414be1333cf6de50f3c712f2f9750b8ea0224ce","tid":627302,"uid":55851,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"b72d153c86a3cb09a626ebe2953f4dc0c2ecdcfd","tid":627302,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":3,"s